boomer
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:anything very large of its kind (esp. a lie) (often prefixed with an intensifying or hypocoristic little).
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: ca1935 Havelock (mainly among older people of second generation back, but still occas.
